com.mumfrey.liteloader.api

Interface Listener

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    ChatFilter, ChatListener, ChatRenderListener, CommonPluginChannelListener, EntityRenderListener, FrameBufferListener, GameLoopListener, HUDRenderListener, InitCompleteListener, JoinGameListener, LiteMod, Messenger, OutboundChatFilter, OutboundChatListener, PacketHandler, Permissible, PlayerClickListener, PlayerInteractionListener, PlayerMoveListener, PluginChannelListener, PostLoginListener, PostRenderListener, PreJoinGameListener, PreRenderListener, RenderListener, ScreenshotListener, ServerChatFilter, ServerCommandProvider, ServerPlayerListener, ServerPluginChannelListener, ServerTickable, ShutdownListener, Tickable, ViewportListener
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    PermissibleAllMods, PermissionsManagerClient, PermissionsManagerServer

    public interface Listener
    LiteLoader Extensible API - Listener is the base interface for (counter-intuitively) consumable Listener interfaces, in that derived interfaces are consumable (from the point of view of the providers) but actual implementors consume the events thus advertised by implementing those interfaces, making them themselves the consumers. Okay so that's probably pretty confusing but I can't think of any better terminology so it's staying :)
    Author:
    Adam Mummery-Smith
